data.description: Rare offering in  Elk Ridge Farms sitting on a private 1.21 Acre Cul De Sac  Homesite that backs up to 57 gorgeous Acres of protected woodlands,  in the highly sought after Avon Grove School District.  This beautifully appointed 4 Bedroom 2.1 bath home features almost 3600 Sq. Ft. of Living space, with grand room sizes and an open Floor plan.  As you enter the Home there is a huge Foyer that features Hardwood floors and overlooks the T-Shaped staircase,  the Foyer is flanked by the formal Living & Dining Rooms, feature colonial Millwork.  The hardwoods lead you into the  Heart of the Home, the vast Kitchen & breakfast room  which features Center Island Breakfast bar with a Butcher Block Top,  42" Raised Panel "Century" cabinets  w/ base cabinet Rollouts,  Lazy Susan, Pantry cabinet, a Tile backsplash  and all newly upgraded Appliances, which include a French Door S/S Refrigerator, Ceramic Top  Convection Range & Microwave,  plus a Bosch Dishwasher.  There is a Pass through to a very  flexible and bright  Morning Room highlighted with Transom windows, Ceiling Fan light &  outstanding views of the countryside.  Loads of recessed lighting throughout this vast area. Let's not forget the huge Family room with Gas Fireplace, w/ colonial Mantle & Slate surround,  highlighted with two eyeball lights.  The home does feature a private first floor Den/Office as well. The Second floor features a huge Primary Bedroom with  a double door entry,  a sitting or dressing area,  volume tray ceiling w/ recessed lighting. There is a Four piece tile bath with a soaking tub, newly installed Tile shower w/ niche & glass doors plus a double sink & dressing table with comfort height vanity,  private water closet, and one of two walk-ins closets. The secondary bedrooms are all extremely well sized for that growing Family,  all bedrooms have Ceiling Fan outlets ,plus there is a loft or playroom area, that affords you more flexibility for the children's living space needs as they grow and aspire.  Lastly a step saving laundry room  with a storage closet and Washer/Dryer included. There is also a walk out, unfinished/daylit Basement space w/ a  full bath rough-in waiting for your finishing touch.  Major System Upgrades include High "E" propane,  two zone Heat w/  two newer Air conditioners(installed in 21' & 22',) High "E" propane Hot water heater (installed in 23')  A brand new  "Certainteed" Dimensional Shake Roof (installed in 23')  The entire Home was just Professionally Painted from top to bottom.  All new upgraded Carpet and Padding were just installed throughout the Home, as well.  Loads of recessed Lighting, all Appliances Convey, oversized side entry Garage.
